Package com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.internal.directconnectivity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Address
    Used internally to represent a physical address in the Azure DocumentDB database service.
    AddressCache  
    AddressInformation
    Used internally to encapsulate a physical address information in the Azure DocumentDB database service.
    ConsistencyReader
    Used internally to provides store reading functionality for all consistency levels in the Azure DocumentDB database service.
    GatewayAddressCache
    Used internally to cache the physical addresses of the collections' partitions in the Azure DocumentDB database service.
    GoneAndRetryWithRetryPolicy
    Used internally to represents a retry policy for Gone exception in the Azure DocumentDB database service.
    HttpClientFactory
    Used internally to represents a factory to create HttpClient to communicate with the Azure DocumentDB database service.
    HttpTransportClient
    Used internally to represents the transport client that communicates with the Azure DocumentDB database service.
    ServerStoreModel
    Used internally to provides functionality to communicate and process response in direct connectivity mode in the Azure DocumentDB database service.
    StoreReadResult
    Used internally to represent a result of a read request from the store.
    StoreResponse
    Used internally to represents a response from the store.
    TransportClient
